ir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="约翰尼·蓝天 (Johnny Blue Skies) 的《Passage Du Desir》专辑封面。信用出版社" width="2000" height="2007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x803.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1397.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1072.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763365" class="wp-caption-text">约翰尼·蓝天 (Johnny Blue Skies) 的《Passage Du Desir》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“Passage Du Desir”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.《悲伤沼泽》</strong><br /> <strong>2.《如果太阳不再升起》</strong><br /> <strong>3.《踏板车蓝调》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《木星的精灵》</strong><br /> <strong>5.《我是谁》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“正确的梦想”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“薄荷茶”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“一条路”</strong></p><p>辛普森此前在与<a href="/artists/diplo">Diplo</a>和 Dove Cameron 合作制作 2023 年曲目“Use Me (Brutal Hearts)”时使用了 Johnny Blue Skies 的绰号。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Diplo - Use Me（残酷之心）[官方视频]壮举。约翰尼·蓝天和德芙·卡梅隆" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_OX3uUhgusM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 